 prayers, nor his fasting, nor his good deeds. He will say: O Lord, this is the record\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24889,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/mujahid-kadhib-ghibah-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":24885,"position":1},"title":"Mujahid on Fasting: Backbiting and lies harm fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Layth reported: Mujahid, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever is safe from two characteristics will secure his fasting: backbiting and falsehood.\u201d Al-Bayhaqi said, \"Just as one guards his fasting from what is not befitting, one must guard himself in the month of Ramadan to obey Allah as much\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/29\/easiest-fasting-not-eating\/","url_meta":{"origin":24885,"position":2},"title":"Maymun on Siyam: Easiest part of fasting is not eating or drinking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ja\u2019far reported: Maymun ibn Mihran, may Allah have mercy on him, would say, \u201cVerily, the easiest part of fasting is leaving food and drink.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 3380 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0648\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u0650\u0647\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0643\u0627\u0646\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u062a\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0643\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 3380 \u0634\u0639\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646 \u0644\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064a\u0627\u0645\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/06\/true-fasting-leave-bad-words\/","url_meta":{"origin":24885,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sawm: True fasting is leaving sins, bad words","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Whoever does not leave evil words and deeds while fasting, Allah does not need him to leave food and drink.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1903 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26196,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/07\/ibn-sireen-rulers-your-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":24885,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Sireen on Tyrants: Your sins worse for you than Ruler\u2019s crimes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 7, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Haytham ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: Ibn Sirin, may Allah be pleased with him, heard a man cursing Al-Hajjaj, so he said, \u201cCalm down, sir! When you arrive in the Hereafter, the smallest sins you committed will be worse for you than the greatest sins committed by Al-Hajjaj. Know that Allah judges\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/shield-damaged-gheebah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24885,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sins of tongue damage fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Ubaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield, as long as you do not damage it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2235 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\